      "comment": "VITO'S POOLISH (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 5 lengths from the winner (30.00). Rates on top in this line up. ZIPPING EVANIA (6) has a strong overall record having 14 wins and 25 places from 51 starts including a last start third (29.93) over 515m at this track. Will go close here with a clear run. GREAT CHAT (7) was out of the placings latest but three back was a Grade 5 winner in quick time (29.59) at Richmond in a Grade 5. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to do much better this time. REAL BONNIE (8) generally performs well over this distance.",
